chunks.title: Shipping Information
chunks.text: All orders are processed within 24 hours and delivered within 3 to 5 business days. Express shipping options are available at checkout for an additional fee.

chunks.title: Company Overview
chunks.text: We are a technology-driven company specializing in AI automation, customer support chatbots, and cloud-based business solutions. Our mission is to simplify digital transformation for small and medium businesses.

chunks.title: Service Packages
chunks.text: We offer three main packages to meet the needs of different customer types. BASIC PACKAGE: The Basic Package is ideal for individuals or small startups. It includes access to our chatbot system, email support, and up to 500 monthly inquiries. This plan does not include analytics or customization options. STANDARD PACKAGE: The Standard Package is designed for small to medium businesses. It includes everything in the Basic Package plus access to the admin dashboard, usage analytics, and up to 5,000 monthly inquiries. This plan also includes limited customization features and priority email support. PREMIUM PACKAGE: The Premium Package is our most comprehensive plan.

chunks.title: Service Packages
chunks.text: It includes everything in the Standard Package along with full customization, API access, unlimited inquiries, dedicated account management, and 24/7 priority support. This package is recommended for enterprise clients or businesses with high-volume customer interactions. ADDITIONAL NOTES: All packages can be billed monthly or annually, with a 20% discount for yearly subscriptions. Upgrading or downgrading between packages can be done at any time from the admin dashboard.

chunks.title: Business Hours
chunks.text: Our business is open from Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM. We are closed on weekends and public holidays.
